Name: Fantasy Dungeon

Explore fascinating levels full of various monsters and and farm coins. Prove that you are a real hero! The game will help you to have fun while spending spare time you don't have... Game Features: 50+ different locations 15 types of monsters ready to kill you cruelly Many unique weapon available in the shop Steam Achievements support Amazing soundtrack Some situations can be hardcore!
